        <h2>Security & Privacy Model</h2>
        <div class="section-number">06</div>
      </div>
      <div class="two-col">
        <div>
          <h3>Security: Phishing-Resistant, Zero-Trust</h3>
          <p>Passkey-primary authentication, DPoP token binding, device attestation, mTLS, and PAR‚Äîsecure-by-default at every layer.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
